            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1276424</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>SteelSeries 近日推出了一款专为 PlayStation 设计的无线耳机「Arctis GameBuds」，这款真无线耳机同时支援蓝牙 5.3 与 2.4GHz 高速无线转接器，在游戏机使用时可享受超低延迟的音响；而切换到蓝牙模式后，又可直接连接智能手机、电脑，可说是相当方便。以下小编就会做更详细评测，看看耳机整体表现。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>2.4GHz 转接器同蓝牙两用</h2><p>就如刚才提及，SteelSeries Arctis GameBuds 支援 2.4GHz 高速无线转接器。在充电盒内，你可找到一个 USB-C 介面的手指。只要将它插上 PlayStation 游戏机的 USB-C 接口，就可在耳机上听到游戏机的音响。耳机咪高锋亦可作游戏、聊天室内的通话用途。转接器模式、蓝牙模式切换很方便，预设设定中，用家只要按 3 下右边耳机上的按钮便可。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276429" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲连接游戏机的 2.4GHz 无线转接器，基本解决玩游戏时的声音延迟问题</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276430" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲安装于 PS5 的 USB-C 插口便可</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲你可在手机 App 中找到不同 PlayStation 游戏专用设定，在不同游戏中享有特别的专用声效调校。配合 3D 效果，在游戏中可以好清晰感应到敌人的定位；</p><p>这个 USB-C 无线音响转接器除了能用于 PlayStation 游戏机外，也能应用于 Nintendo Switch 游戏机、电脑（包括 Windows/Mac 电脑）、iPhone 或 Android 智能电话、VR 装置，但就不适用于 Xbox 游戏机。只要将转接器插上电脑、电话、游戏机上的 USB-C 插口，在装置上选取使用 Arctis GameBuds 输出音讯即可使用。而除了 USB-C 之外，耳机随附一个 USB-C 至 USB-A 转接器，方便连接较旧电脑。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在 Nintendo Switch 使用时可辨认为 USB 音响</p><p>当然如果你的电脑、智能电话内置蓝牙功能，就可用 Arctis GameBuds 的蓝牙模式连接。在耳机上，连续按三下耳机上的按钮，即可切换转接器模式／蓝牙模式。在晚间享受游戏，你更可使用 Arctis GameBuds 内置的主动降噪、透明模式。耳机内置有 4 咪高风结合 ANC 技术，过滤外界噪音。而在透明模式让你在需要时，听取周围环境声音。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>超过 100 款 PS5 游戏的音效预设档</h2><p>配合 iOS／Android 的耳机专用 Arctis Companion 手机程式，你可切换超过 100 种音效设定，包括很多 PS5 游戏，实时专门为该游戏调整的音效，以增强沉浸感。我们就尝试过《The Last of Us II》《Gran Turismo 7》，在紧凑的冒险游戏、赛车游戏都很准确定位来自于四面八方的声音。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在试玩赛车游戏也能体验到很强重低音音效，以及分辨到其他对手的定位</p><br /><b>
]]>
